### Health check
GET {{host}}/
Accept: application/json

### Create Participant - Athlete (Swimming, USA)
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "1234567",
  "type": "Athlete",
  "givenName": "Katie",
  "familyName": "Ledecky",
  "genderCode": "F",
  "birthDate": "1997-03-17",
  "noc": "USA"
}

