### Get Participant by ID
GET {{host}}/api/participants/1234567
Accept: application/json

### Get Participant (not found)
GET {{host}}/api/participants/9999999
Accept: application/json

### List Participants by NOC - USA
GET {{host}}/api/participants/by-noc/USA
Accept: application/json

### List Participants by NOC - Jamaica
GET {{host}}/api/participants/by-noc/JAM
Accept: application/json

### List Participants by NOC (empty result)
GET {{host}}/api/participants/by-noc/ZZZ
Accept: application/json

### Validation: empty participantId
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "",
  "type": "Athlete",
  "givenName": "Test",
  "familyName": "User",
  "genderCode": "M",
  "noc": "USA"
}

### Validation: invalid type
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "9999999",
  "type": "InvalidType",
  "givenName": "Test",
  "familyName": "User",
  "genderCode": "M",
  "noc": "USA"
}

### Validation: invalid gender code
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "9999998",
  "type": "Athlete",
  "givenName": "Test",
  "familyName": "User",
  "genderCode": "Z",
  "noc": "USA"
}

### Validation: NOC too short
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "9999997",
  "type": "Athlete",
  "givenName": "Test",
  "familyName": "User",
  "genderCode": "M",
  "noc": "US"
}

### Conflict: duplicate participant
# Run after creating participant 1234567
POST {{host}}/api/participants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "participantId": "1234567",
  "type": "Athlete",
  "givenName": "Another",
  "familyName": "Person",
  "genderCode": "M",
  "noc": "USA"
}
